thor":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTwo qualities are never combined in a believer: miserliness and bad character.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1962 Grade:\u00a0Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064f\u062f\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8039,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/13\/bad-neighbors-yawm-al-qiyamah\/","url_meta":{"origin":19181,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Neighbors: How many bad neighbors on Judgment Day?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHow many neighbors will be brought with their neighbors on the Day of Resurrection? One will say: O Lord, this man closed his door to me and refused to show courtesy!\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 111\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26975,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/12\/30\/disease-of-nations\/","url_meta":{"origin":19181,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ummah: The Prophet warns against diseases of nations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 30, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, the diseases of nations will afflict my nation.\" They said, \"O Messenger of Allah, what are the diseases of nations?\" The Prophet said, \"Insolence, hubris, turning their backs to one another, competing for worldly possessions,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41356,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/10\/05\/hellfire-arrogance-miserliness\/","url_meta":{"origin":19181,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Kibr: Hellfire full of arrogant, miserly people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said upon mention of the inhabitants of Hellfire, \u201cIt is everyone cruel, haughty, arrogant, a hoarder of possessions, and a withholder of good.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 6580 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u0650\u0648\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33743,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/20\/salah-ummah-zuhd\/","url_meta":{"origin":19181,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ummah: Righteousness in temperance, destruction in worldly hope","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe rightness in the beginning of this nation was by renouncing the world and attaining conviction. The destruction in the end of it is by miserliness and vain hopes.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd li-Ah\u0323mad ibn H\u0323anbal 52\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43304,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/22\/faith-not-coexist-avarice\/","url_meta":{"origin":19181,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Greed: Faith does not coexist with avarice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 22, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGreed and faith are never combined within the heart of a servant.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304\u2019i\u0304 3109 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u00a0\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u062c\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0645\u0